==English==
==Etymology==
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] prefix '''[[προ-]]''' (''pro-'') "in front of, position before, priority of rank", from '''[[πρό]]''' (''pro'') "before, forth, rather than".

===Prefix===
'''pro-'''
# [[agreeing]] with; [[supporting]]; [[favouring]]
# [[substituting]] for
# [[earlier]]; [[prior]]
# [[rudimentary]]
# in [[front]] of
